desc: Walkabout Harnesses are the best dog harnesses for mobility and stability. Founded by a vet and vet-approved means these pet harnesses are a medical favorite. Looking for a dog knee brace, a dog harness for a 3-legged dog, or a dog sling? Walkabout Harnesses have a range of products to help.

layout.text: Walkabout Harnesses: Support harnesses, boots and braces for your pet.
